HEADWORD: Exclusionist
<hw>Ex*clu"sion*ist</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>One who would exclude
another from some right or privilege; esp., one of the anti-popish
politicians of the time of Charles II.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

